This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it discusses 3D object recognition. It is also likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it uses convolutional neural networks. The use of CNNs also suggests it could belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the mention of 2D and 3D lattices suggests it could belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
